snippet.title: Citadel Warrior for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

In Citadel Warrior the objective is to collect all cyclotrons. 

You will constantly run out fuels and the only way to replenish it is by standing on a platform which says "fuel".

Laser barriers will suck the fuel out and once you are out fuel you die.


What I think:

Not bad, but the sounds and the music are bad.

Speaking of the music...is it just me or does the beginning sound like the beginng of the Great Giana Sisters theme?
